name: PROPERTIES 06 - House in Little Tokio
description:
The following NFT corresponds to the collection of properties located in Kitty City in the Little Tokio neighborhood.
This property maintains 2 fully luminous floors, from the upper floor you can see the forest of 100 pink bonsai and the outskirts of the Little Nostalgia neighborhood. This place invites you to enjoy the outdoors and the relaxing sound of the river.
Land measurements: 60m x 80m
